							<p class="text-gray-600">
								Refinancing to a 15-year mortgage can save you significant money in total interest and help you build equity faster. However, monthly payments will be higher. This makes sense if you can comfortably afford the higher payments and want to pay off your home sooner or save on total interest costs.
